label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 5 ug of cRNA were hybridized on U133A GeneChip following the recommended procedures. GeneChips were washed and stained according to Affymetrix protocol EukGE-2v4.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using an Affymetrix GeneChip Scanner (Agilent).
